{
    "name": "Intelligent Real Estate Valuation Workflow",
    "nodes": [
        {
            "parameters": {
                "content": "## 1. Multi-Channel Input\n[Ingestion Layer]",
                "height": 400,
                "width": 300,
                "color": 4
            },
            "name": "Sticky Note 1",
            "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
            "typeVersion": 1,
            "position": [
                0,
                200
            ],
            "id": "sticky-note-1"
        },
        {
            "parameters": {
                "httpMethod": "POST",
                "path": "valuation",
                "options": {}
            },
            "name": "Webhook Trigger",
            "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
            "typeVersion": 1,
            "position": [
                50,
                300
            ],
            "id": "webhook-trigger"
        },
        {
            "parameters": {},
            "name": "Manual Chat Trigger",
            "type": "n8n-nodes-base.manualTrigger",
            "typeVersion": 1,
            "position": [
                50,
                500
            ],
            "id": "manual-trigger"
        },
        {
            "parameters": {
                "content": "## 2. Sensory Processing\n[Sensors & Normalization]",
                "height": 500,
                "width": 300,
                "color": 4
            },
            "name": "Sticky Note 2",
            "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
            "typeVersion": 1,
            "position": [
                500,
                150
            ],
            "id": "sticky-note-2"
        },
        {
            "parameters": {
                "dataType": "binary",
                "rule": {
                    "interval": [
                        {
                            "field": "mimeType",
                            "operator": "regex",
                            "value": "audio/.*"
                        },
                        {
                            "field": "mimeType",
                            "operator": "regex",
                            "value": "application/pdf|image/.*"
                        }
                    ]
                }
            },
            "name": "Router (Switch)",
            "type": "n8n-nodes-base.switch",
            "typeVersion": 1,
            "position": [
                550,
                400
            ],
            "id": "router-sensors"
        },
        {
            "parameters": {
                "resource": "audio",
                "operation": "transcribe",
                "binaryPropertyName": "data"
            },
            "name": "Whisper (Audio)",
            "type": "n8n-nodes-base.openAi",
            "typeVersion": 1,
            "position": [
                600,
                250
            ],
            "id": "whisper-node",
            "credentials": {
                "openAiApi": {
                    "id": "YOUR_OPENAI_CREDENTIAL_ID",
                    "name": "OpenAI account"
                }
            }
        },
        {
            "parameters": {
                "model": "gpt-4-vision-preview",
                "prompt": "Extract all text and visual data from this image/document for real estate valuation.",
                "binaryPropertyName": "data"
            },
            "name": "Vision/OCR Node",
            "type": "n8n-nodes-base.openAi",
            "typeVersion": 1,
            "position": [
                600,
                400
            ],
            "id": "vision-node",
            "credentials": {
                "openAiApi": {
                    "id": "YOUR_OPENAI_CREDENTIAL_ID",
                    "name": "OpenAI account"
                }
            }
        },
        {
            "parameters": {
                "content": "## 3. Valuation Hub\n[The Brain]",
                "height": 300,
                "width": 300,
                "color": 6
            },
            "name": "Sticky Note 3",
            "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
            "typeVersion": 1,
            "position": [
                1000,
                350
            ],
            "id": "sticky-note-3"
        },
        {
            "parameters": {
                "model": "gpt-4o",
                "options": {
                    "systemMessage": "### ROLE:\nYou are an expert RICS Chartered Surveyor and Senior Financial Analyst specializing in the [Saudi Arabia / Egypt] real estate market. Your objective is to transform unstructured inputs (Voice Transcripts, OCR from PDFs, or Text Messages) into a professional, structured valuation dataset.\n\n### TASK:\n1. Analyze the input to extract core property details.\n2. Apply the four valuation dimensions (Market, Cost, DCF, and Residual).\n3. Use your internal market intelligence to provide an independent AI benchmark.\n\n### VALUATION METHODS & ESTIMATION PROTOCOL:\n1. **Market Approach:** Identify location and area to estimate the value based on comparable sales.\n2. **Income Approach (DCF):** - Extract NOI, Cap Rate, and Growth. \n   - If missing, ESTIMATE based on 2026 market standards: Discount Rate (10-14%), Growth (3-5%), and Projection Years (5-10).\n3. **Residual Method (For Development Land):**\n   - Estimate Gross Development Value (GDV), Construction Costs, and Developer Profit (target ~20%) if not explicitly provided.\n4. **AI MARKET INTELLIGENCE (Generative Benchmark):**\n   - Provide an independent value estimate based purely on your internal training data regarding specific neighborhood trends, infrastructure projects, and economic sentiment in [Location].\n   - Justify this value in the \"ai_benchmark_reasoning\" field in Arabic.\n\n### OPERATIONAL RULES:\n- **Gap Filling:** If a numerical value is not provided, estimate it and append an asterisk (*) to the key in the \"estimated_fields\" list.\n- **Number Formatting:** Convert words to integers (e.g., \"Two Million\" -> 2000000). Remove currency symbols and units.\n- **Date Formatting:** Use DD/MM/YYYY.\n- **Language:** Maintain Arabic for location names and reasoning descriptions, but use English for keys and numerical data.\n\n### OUTPUT SCHEMA (STRICT JSON ONLY):\n{\n  \"timestamp\": \"DD/MM/YYYY\",\n  \"source_client\": \"String\",\n  \"property_type\": \"String\",\n  \"location_zone\": \"String (Arabic)\",\n  \"area_sqm\": Number,\n  \"valuation_data\": {\n    \"market_approach_value\": Number,\n    \"cost_approach_value\": Number,\n    \"income_dcf_data\": {\n       \"noi_annual\": Number,\n       \"cap_rate_percent\": Number,\n       \"discount_rate_percent\": Number,\n       \"growth_rate_percent\": Number,\n       \"exit_yield_percent\": Number,\n       \"projection_years\": Number\n    },\n    \"residual_data\": {\n       \"gdv\": Number,\n       \"dev_cost\": Number,\n       \"dev_profit_percent\": Number,\n       \"residual_land_value\": Number\n    }\n  },\n  \"ai_generative_benchmark\": {\n    \"ai_suggested_value\": Number,\n    \"ai_benchmark_reasoning\": \"String (Arabic)\"\n  },\n  \"final_reconciled_value\": Number,\n  \"ai_notes\": \"String (Arabic)\",\n  \"estimated_fields\": [\"List\", \"of\", \"estimated\", \"keys\"]\n}",
                    "responseFormat": "json_object"
                }
            },
            "name": "OpenAI Node",
            "type": "n8n-nodes-base.openAi",
            "typeVersion": 1,
            "position": [
                1050,
                400
            ],
            "id": "openai-node",
            "credentials": {
                "openAiApi": {
                    "id": "YOUR_OPENAI_CREDENTIAL_ID",
                    "name": "OpenAI account"
                }
            }
        },
        {
            "parameters": {
                "content": "## 4. Math Engine\n[Logic Layer]",
                "height": 300,
                "width": 300,
                "color": 1
            },
            "name": "Sticky Note 4",
            "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
            "typeVersion": 1,
            "position": [
                1500,
                350
            ],
            "id": "sticky-note-4"
        },
        {
            "parameters": {
                "jsCode": "const aiData = items[0].json;\nconst noi = parseFloat(aiData.valuation_data.income_dcf_data.noi_annual) || 0;\nconst discountRate = parseFloat(aiData.valuation_data.income_dcf_data.discount_rate_percent) / 100 || 0.12;\nconst growthRate = parseFloat(aiData.valuation_data.income_dcf_data.growth_rate_percent) / 100 || 0.03;\nconst exitYield = parseFloat(aiData.valuation_data.income_dcf_data.exit_yield_percent) / 100 || 0.08;\nconst years = parseInt(aiData.valuation_data.income_dcf_data.projection_years) || 5;\n\nlet totalNPV = 0;\nlet runningNoi = noi;\nfor (let t = 1; t <= years; t++) {\n    runningNoi *= (1 + growthRate);\n    totalNPV += runningNoi / Math.pow((1 + discountRate), t);\n}\nconst terminalValue = (runningNoi * (1 + growthRate)) / exitYield;\nconst finalDCF = totalNPV + (terminalValue / Math.pow((1 + discountRate), years));\n\nreturn [{ json: { ...aiData, calculated_dcf_final: Math.round(finalDCF), calculation_status: \"Validated\" } }];"
            },
            "name": "JS Engine",
            "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
            "typeVersion": 2,
            "position": [
                1550,
                400
            ],
            "id": "js-engine"
        },
        {
            "parameters": {
                "content": "## 5. Master Database\n[Archive Layer]",
                "height": 300,
                "width": 300,
                "color": 3
            },
            "name": "Sticky Note 5",
            "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
            "typeVersion": 1,
            "position": [
                2000,
                350
            ],
            "id": "sticky-note-5"
        },
        {
            "parameters": {
                "operation": "append",
                "sheetId": "YOUR_GOOGLE_SHEET_ID",
                "range": "A:V",
                "options": {}
            },
            "name": "Google Sheets",
            "type": "n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets",
            "typeVersion": 4,
            "position": [
                2050,
                400
            ],
            "id": "google-sheets",
            "credentials": {
                "googleSheetsOAuth2Api": {
                    "id": "YOUR_GOOGLE_SHEETS_CREDENTIAL_ID",
                    "name": "Google Sheets account"
                }
            }
        }
    ],
